here last class.

00:51:09.400 --> 00:51:11.367
But just to summarize,
the Doppler cooling rate

00:51:11.367 --> 00:51:12.908
gets us to a
temperature on the order

00:51:12.908 --> 00:51:14.330
of gamma, which is
natural alignment.

00:51:14.330 --> 00:51:14.955
PROFESSOR: Yes.

00:51:14.955 --> 00:51:18.936
AUDIENCE: And the recoil
limit is the recoil energy

00:51:18.936 --> 00:51:21.870
which is usually
